nodes.text: This Individual was a male Mandalorian mercenary and leader of a clan of Mandalorians on Nar Shaddaa during the Dark Wars. When the Jedi Exile, Meetra Surik, came to the planet, she with Mandalore the Preserver, encountered this clan. While he had shown to be a little hostile towards outsiders, he was welcoming to Mandalorians when he had mistaken Mandalore for another mercenary. He was eventually convinced by Meetra to join the other clans on Dxun.
